s=\"lucide lucide-mail text-[var(--primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Email</h3><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">contact@naturegren.com</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[30px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[#edf6e8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin text-[var(--primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Address</h3><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Dallas,Irving ,Texas,USA</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[30px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[#edf6e8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock text-[var(--primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Working Hours</h3><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">24/7 Support</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"contact-form\" class=\"bg-white py-28\"><div class=\"\n        mx-auto\n        w-full\n        max-w-[1320px]\n        px-5\n        lg:px-8\n        \n      \"><div class=\"grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr]\"><div><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[var(--primary)]\">Send Inquiry</span><h2 class=\"mt-5 font-serif text-5xl leading-tight text-[var(--text)]\">Let&#x27;s Start<br/>A Conversation</h2><p class=\"mt-8 text-lg leading-8 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Have questions about our handcrafted jute products, wholesale pricing, exports or custom manufacturing? Fill out the form and our team will respond shortly.</p><div class=\"mt-12 rounded-[28px] bg-[#fcfaf7] p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Why Contact NatureGren?</h3><ul class=\"mt-6 space-y-4 text-[var(--text-muted)]\"><li>✓ Bulk &amp; Wholesale Orders</li><li>✓ Export Partnerships</li><li>✓ Corporate Gifting</li><li>✓ Custom Product Development</li></ul></div></div><form class=\"rounded-[32px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-[#fcfaf7] p-10 shadow-lg\"><div class=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2\"><input placeholder=\"Full Name\" required=\"\" class=\"h-14 rounded-xl border px-5 outline-none focus:border-[var(--primary)]\"/><input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Email Address\" required=\"\" class=\"h-14 rounded-xl border px-5 outline-none focus:border-[var(--primary)]\"/><input placeholder=\"Phone Number\" class=\"h-14 rounded-xl border px-5 outline-none focus:border-[var(--primary)]\"/><input placeholder=\"Company\" class=\"h-14 rounded-xl border px-5 outline-none focus:border-[var(--primary)]\"/></div><input placeholder=\"Subject\" class=\"mt-6 h-14 w-full rounded-xl border px-5 outline-none focus:border-[var(--primary)]\"/><textarea rows=\"7\" placeholder=\"Tell us about your requirements...\" class=\"mt-6 w-full rounded-xl border p-5 outline-none focus:border-[var(--primary)]\"></textarea><button type=\"submit\" class=\" mt-8 h-14 w-full rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)] font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[var(--primary-hover)] disabled:opacity-60 \">Send Inquiry</button></form></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-[#fcfaf7] py-28\"><div class=\"\n        mx-auto\n        w-full\n        max-w-[1320px]\n        px-5\n        lg:px-8\n        \n      \"><div class=\"grid gap-14 lg:grid-cols-[0.45fr_0.55fr]\"><div><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[var(--primary)]\">Visit Us</span><h2 class=\"mt-5 font-serif text-5xl leading-tight text-[var(--text)]\">Our Office &amp;<br/>Manufacturing Hub</h2><p class=\"mt-8 text-lg leading-8 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">We&#x27;d love to welcome you. Schedule a visit to discuss wholesale orders, exports, custom manufacturing or explore our handcrafted jute collections.</p><div class=\"mt-10 rounded-[28px] bg-white p-8 shadow-md\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-[#edf6e8] p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin text-[var(--primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">NatureGren</h3><p class=\"mt-2 leading-7 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Biratnagar,<br/>Koshi Province,<br/>Nepal</p></div></div><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Biratnagar,+Koshi+Province,+Nepal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\" mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)] px-6 py-3 text-white transition hover:bg-[var(--primary-hover)] \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-navigation\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polygon points=\"3 11 22 2 13 21 11 13 3 11\"></polygon></svg>Open in Google Maps</a></div></div><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-[32px] shadow-xl\"><iframe title=\"NatureGren Location\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps?q=Biratnagar,Koshi,Nepal&amp;output=embed\" class=\"h-[520px] w-full border-0\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerPolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white py-28\"><div class=\"\n        mx-auto\n        w-full\n        max-w-[1320px]\n        px-5\n        lg:px-8\n        \n      \"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl\"><div class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[var(--primary)]\">FAQ</span><h2 class=\"mt-5 font-serif text-5xl text-[var(--text)]\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Answers to the questions we receive most often from our customers and business partners.</p></div><div class=\"mt-16 space-y-5\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-[24px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-[#fcfaf7]\"><button class=\"flex w-full items-center justify-between p-7 text-left\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Do you accept bulk and wholesale orders?</h3><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-300 rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"px-7 pb-7\"><p class=\"leading-8 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Yes. We manufacture and supply bulk quantities for wholesalers, retailers, exporters and corporate clients.</p></div></div><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-[24px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-[#fcfaf7]\"><button class=\"flex w-full items-center justify-between p-7 text-left\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Can I customize products with my own branding?</h3><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-[24px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-[#fcfaf7]\"><button class=\"flex w-full items-center justify-between p-7 text-left\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Do you export internationally?</h3><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-[24px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-[#fcfaf7]\"><button class=\"flex w-full items-center justify-between p-7 text-left\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">What materials do you use?</h3><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-[24px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-[#fcfaf7]\"><button class=\"flex w-full items-center justify-between p-7 text-left\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">How long does production take?</h3><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill